{"tid":2004024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 行程滿檔　7 月初在日本回歸！","createTime":"2020-05-06T07:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T09:42:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d555692526f2dc96564bc0a22de330282d4dacb9","tid":2004024,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"準備於 6 月在韓國回歸的 TWICE，隔月也將發行時隔不到半年的日語新作品，即將接連登場的活動讓人期待不已！<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 昨晚（5 日）在官方推特上閃電公開一支影片，並親自宣布她們將於 7 月 8 日在日本發表第六張單曲〈Fanfare〉。是一首 TWICE 想藉由〈Fanfare〉為世界帶來正面力量，也會透過現場表演也展現活力十足的面貌。<br />\n<br />\n除了宣布好消息外，TWICE 也表示：「好想趕快見到大家，希望到時候都能看到大家健健康康的。我們最近也有注意維持身體健康，大家都加油！」<br />\n<br />\n自從在日本出道以來，TWICE 發行的每張專輯銷量都超過 25 萬張，已在當地奠定難以取代的地位。在 TWICE 回歸前，就先重溫她們在年初推出的日語改版專輯吧！"},{"pid":"3bccbb5c845f9ce24be641ed7111844a03dbf81d","tid":2004024,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_42b3756c83726172fbd262d5baab8d4d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-05-06/126486-837430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_42b3756c83726172fbd262d5baab8d4d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-05-06%2F126486-837430.png&h=cdb0755c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6199705af1b86edf33b5972cd50d8b81baf96c","tid":2004024,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/2570bee6103f1e07660c8db7a6a28029/89118425dfe12669-91/s400x600/0aab52d653b892adc4ebe8b646d0c9c3b7a5c7ff.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F2570bee6103f1e07660c8db7a6a28029%2F89118425dfe12669-91%2Fs400x600%2F0aab52d653b892adc4ebe8b646d0c9c3b7a5c7ff.gifv&h=cb559d68&s={SIZE}\" />